s=\"swp-compact-playlist-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"swp_music_player_entry compact-player-entry clearfix\" data-mediafile=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Advanced-HubSpot-Customization-Tips-for-Small-Businesses.mp3\">\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"swp_song_details player_entry_left\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"play_icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"fas fa-play before_song compact_bs\"><\/i>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"player_song_name transition3\" data-albumname=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"entry_duration mpfe_fix_lh\"><\/span>\t\t\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"song_buy_icons compact_buy_icons transition3 clearfix mobile_visibility_hide\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f533f2f all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f533f2f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-1\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Introduction<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af64877 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"af64877\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Is your small business truly maximizing HubSpot CRM? Many businesses use it, but few take full advantage of its powerful customization options. A well-optimized CRM can streamline operations, improve customer relationships, and increase revenue.<\/p><p>In fact, according to <a href=\"https:\/\/blog.hubspot.com\/marketing\/marketing-automation-benefits\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">studies,<\/a> businesses using CRM automation see a 14.5% boost in sales productivity. Yet, many small businesses struggle to customize their system in a way that fits their unique needs.<\/p><p>In this guide, we\u2019ll break down advanced HubSpot CRM customization tips to help you create a system that works for you. One that tracks the right data improves efficiency and drives growth. Let\u2019s get started.<\/p><p><strong>Key Takeaways<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Customize HubSpot to fit your sales, marketing, and customer service needs.<\/li><li>Use automation to save time and improve follow-ups.<\/li><li>Integrate HubSpot with other tools for a smooth workflow.<\/li><li>Test and optimize forms, pages, and emails for better results.<\/li><li>Get expert help when needed to avoid costly mistakes.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-35cd2d3 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"35cd2d3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-2\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What Is HubSpot CRM?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3d40c60 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3d40c60\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/hubspot\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HubSpot is a customer relationship management (CRM) platform<\/a>. It helps businesses manage contacts, track sales, and automate marketing. Small businesses use HubSpot to organize customer interactions and improve efficiency.<\/p><p>Founded in 2006, HubSpot started as a marketing tool. Today, it offers sales, customer service, and content management solutions. Over 248,000 businesses worldwide use it to grow their customer base.<\/p><p>With HubSpot, you can store leads, track emails, set reminders, and create reports all in one place. It\u2019s easy to use and scales with your business. Whether you&#8217;re managing five customers or five thousand, HubSpot keeps everything organized.<\/p><p>Simply put, it\u2019s a tool that helps businesses grow smarter.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3d08ee1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3d08ee1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/What-Is-HubSpot-CRM-r2312rt4m6kvk81qelpk2w0rykbhnt5mmlmmgm1ik0.jpg\" title=\"What Is HubSpot CRM\" alt=\"What Is HubSpot CRM\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9ce3810 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9ce3810\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-3\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Choose HubSpot for Small Businesses?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a6c489 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0a6c489\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Small businesses need a CRM that is easy to use and helps them grow. HubSpot offers several benefits that make it a great choice:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Free CRM:<\/strong> Many small businesses start with the free plan and upgrade as they grow. It includes contact management, email tracking, and reporting.<\/li><li><strong>Easy Integrations:<\/strong> HubSpot connects with over 1,500 apps, including Gmail, Outlook, Shopify, and QuickBooks. This makes it simple to sync your tools.<\/li><li><strong>Automation:<\/strong> You can automate emails, follow-ups, and tasks. This saves time and helps teams focus on selling.<\/li><li><strong>Reports and Dashboards:<\/strong> HubSpot provides detailed analytics to track leads and sales. Businesses that use CRM reports see a 29% increase in sales.<\/li><li><strong>Customer Support Tools:<\/strong> Live chat, a knowledge base, and ticketing help small businesses respond quickly to customers.<\/li><li><strong>Scalability:<\/strong> Whether you\u2019re a solo entrepreneur or managing a small team, HubSpot grows with your business.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-501f2a0 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"501f2a0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-4\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">HubSpot CRM Customization for Businesses - Advanced Tips<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c7636cf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c7636cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-de05640 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"de05640\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>HubSpot CRM is flexible, but customizing HubSpot for startups ensures it fits unique needs. Here are HubSpot workflow customization tips that small businesses can use to maximize their potential.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-394375d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"394375d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-de05640 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"de05640\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Take your CRM automation even further with <a class=\"in-cell-link\" href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/blog\/hubspot-compatible-ai-agents\/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>HubSpot-compatible AI agents<\/strong><\/a> designed to boost efficiency and smart decision-making.<\/span><\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b0a75f3 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b0a75f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-5\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Define and Align Your Sales Process<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f0daf1a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f0daf1a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A structured sales process makes it easier to track leads and close deals. Start by mapping out your customer journey, from the first interaction to the final sale.<\/p><ul><li>Customize deal stages to match real-world steps. For example, if your business offers consultations, include a &#8220;Consultation Scheduled&#8221; stage.<\/li><li>Assign clear tasks to each stage, such as sending follow-up emails or scheduling calls.<\/li><li>Ensure sales and marketing teams use consistent naming conventions to avoid confusion.<\/li><\/ul><p>According to HubSpot, businesses that organize their sales process see higher conversion rates and better team collaboration.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ab8b22 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8ab8b22\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-6\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Develop Custom Properties<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-38e902d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"38e902d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>HubSpot\u2019s default properties cover the basics, but businesses often need more. Custom properties allow you to track specific details about leads, customers, or sales.<br \/>For example, a subscription-based business might need fields for:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Subscription Type<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Renewal Date<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Payment Status<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Cancellation Reason<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><p>Retailers might want properties for product preferences or order history. Doing this helps you personalize marketing campaigns and improve customer interactions.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c65a461 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c65a461\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-7\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Utilize Custom Objects<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1390e8c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1390e8c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Not every business fits into the standard \u201ccontacts, companies, and deals\u201d structure. That\u2019s where custom objects come in.<br \/>Imagine you run a property management company. You could create a custom object for \u201cRental Properties\u201d and link it to tenants and maintenance requests.<\/p><p>Or, if you\u2019re a manufacturer, you might track product warranties and service requests. With custom objects, businesses can store and manage unique data in a way that makes sense for their operations.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bd7aa08 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"bd7aa08\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/HubSpots-workflow-automation-ensures-follow-ups-r2313oph9dtwukpy2hxi05pwr1tc57s8f4gm9aoqi8.jpg\" title=\"HubSpot\u2019s workflow automation ensures follow-ups\" alt=\"HubSpot\u2019s workflow automation ensures follow-ups\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9680703 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9680703\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-8\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Automate Workflows to Save Time<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a1e3dc7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a1e3dc7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Manual tasks slow teams down. HubSpot\u2019s workflow automation ensures follow-ups, reminders, and updates happen automatically.<\/p><ul><li>Trigger emails when a lead downloads a resource.<\/li><li>Assign tasks to sales reps when a deal moves forward.<\/li><li>Send alerts when customers take key actions, like abandoning a cart.<\/li><li>Update contact properties automatically when a lead reaches a new stage.<\/li><li>Enroll leads in nurturing sequences based on their behavior.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c7201ea all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c7201ea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-9\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Leverage Third-Party Tools and APIs<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d88d98a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d88d98a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>HubSpot integrates with over 1,500 third-party tools, making it easy to connect with other business software.<\/p><ul><li><strong>E-commerce businesses:<\/strong> Sync with Shopify to track customer orders.<\/li><li><strong>Service-based companies:<\/strong> Connect with Calendly to automate appointment scheduling.<\/li><li><strong>Finance teams:<\/strong> Link QuickBooks for seamless invoicing and payment tracking.<\/li><\/ul><p>For businesses with unique needs, HubSpot\u2019s API allows developers to build custom integrations, ensuring all systems work together smoothly.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1cbba13 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1cbba13\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-10\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Customize Dashboards and Reports for Better Insights<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-856eb9c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"856eb9c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Not all businesses need the same data. HubSpot lets you create custom dashboards to focus on what matters most.<\/p><ul><li>Sales teams can track lead conversion rates and deal progress.<br \/>Marketing teams can monitor email performance and website traffic.<\/li><li>Customer service teams can analyze ticket resolution times.<\/li><li>Sales managers can identify top-performing reps and areas needing improvement.<\/li><li>Customer service teams can monitor customer satisfaction scores to improve support strategies.<\/li><\/ul><p>By customizing reports, businesses can spot trends, improve strategies, and make data-driven decisions. According to <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/salesforce\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Salesforce<\/a>, companies that closely track CRM analytics report a significant boost in productivity.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-10b4fbb all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"10b4fbb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-11\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Prioritize Leads with Lead Scoring<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3be20b3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3be20b3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Not all leads are ready to buy. HubSpot\u2019s lead scoring system helps sales teams focus on the most promising prospects.<\/p><ul><li>Assign points for actions like opening emails, visiting key pages, or filling out forms.<\/li><li>Deduct points for inactivity or unsubscribing from emails.<\/li><\/ul><p>Leads with higher scores can be fast-tracked to sales, while lower-scoring leads might need more nurturing.<\/p><p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/blog\/hubspot-crm-implementation\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Learn more: HubSpot CRM Implementation<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b479dbc elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"b479dbc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/HubSpots-CMS-tools-allow-businesses-to-design-websites-and-landing-pages-r2314pd6nx83fd8p4fry7egvx2snhetrk5wjz36drk.jpg\" title=\"HubSpot\u2019s CMS tools allow businesses to design websites and landing pages\" alt=\"HubSpot\u2019s CMS tools allow businesses to design websites and landing pages\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05ae293 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"05ae293\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-12\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Refine Your Website and Landing Pages<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dd093fd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dd093fd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>HubSpot\u2019s CMS tools allow businesses to design websites and landing pages that match their brand.<\/p><p>Instead of generic templates, businesses can:<\/p><ul><li>Use personalized content based on visitor history.<\/li><li>Optimize pages for mobile responsiveness and fast load times.<\/li><li>A\/B test different headlines, images, and CTAs to see what works best.<\/li><li>Use clear navigation to help visitors find information easily and reduce bounce rates.<\/li><li>Integrate chatbots or live chat to engage visitors and answer questions in real time.<\/li><li>Optimize for SEO by including relevant keywords, meta descriptions, and alt text for images.<\/li><li>A well-optimized landing page can boost conversion rates by up to <a href=\"https:\/\/unbounce.com\/average-conversion-rates-landing-pages\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">30%<\/a>.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-082e193 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"082e193\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Improve Forms and Calls-to-Action (CTAs)<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d9393c9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d9393c9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A well-designed form can mean the difference between a lead and a lost visitor.<\/p><p><strong>Here\u2019s what works:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Short, simple forms:<\/strong> Only ask for essential information.<\/li><li><strong>Multi-step forms:<\/strong> Break long forms into sections to improve completion rates.<\/li><li><strong>Engaging CTAs:<\/strong> Use action-driven text like \u201cGet Your Free Guide\u201d instead of \u201cSubmit.\u201d<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca634e3 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ca634e3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Develop a Knowledge Base for Customer Support<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8a645da elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8a645da\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A strong knowledge base reduces customer support requests and improves user experience. Companies that offer self-service support see a reduction in tickets according to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.zendesk.com\/blog\/self-service-decrease-ticket-volume\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">studies<\/a>.<\/p><p><strong>So businesses should:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Create FAQ pages, how-to guides, and troubleshooting articles.<\/li><li>Use videos and step-by-step visuals to improve clarity.<\/li><li>Keep content updated based on common customer questions.<\/li><li>A well-maintained knowledge base not only helps customers but also frees up support teams for more complex issues.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cbc9682 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"cbc9682\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Common-Customization-Mistakes-to-Avoid-r23176nup6mc2bmzn0dia9xocokisno9kfvokdhzcg.jpg\" title=\"Common Customization Mistakes to Avoid\" alt=\"Common Customization Mistakes to Avoid\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b4a9e1 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1b4a9e1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-13\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Common Customization Mistakes to Avoid<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1457d1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1457d1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Adding Too Many Custom Fields<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6ba1742 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6ba1742\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>It\u2019s tempting to track everything, but too many fields slow people down. Sales teams might skip them or, worse, enter random data just to move on. Keep only what\u2019s necessary.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ed4b539 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ed4b539\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Not Training Your Team<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d1855ea elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d1855ea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A system is only useful if people know how to use it. If employees don\u2019t get proper training, they\u2019ll stick to old habits or make mistakes. Walk them through key features and updates.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3a5ae20 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3a5ae20\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Making Workflows Too Complicated<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a648ce9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a648ce9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Automation is great until it creates more problems than it solves. If workflows have too many steps, things break, and tasks get stuck. Keep it simple and easy to follow.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-00d4434 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"00d4434\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Tired of manual file uploads? Discover <a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/blog\/how-to-automate-google-drive-file-integration-with-hubspot-records\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"707\" data-end=\"869\">how to integrate Google Drive files with HubSpot automatically<\/a> and save hours each week.<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a376607 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a376607\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Ignoring Data Clean-Up<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eeb031d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eeb031d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Outdated contacts, duplicate records, and missing details can turn a great system into a mess. Review and clean your data regularly to keep things running smoothly.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66c9b25 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"66c9b25\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Forgetting About Mobile Users<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a446805 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a446805\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>If your team works on the go, they need a system that works on their phones. If dashboards, reports, and forms don\u2019t load well, they won\u2019t get used. Always test on mobile.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5044096 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5044096\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Ignoring Reports and Insights<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bdaadb6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bdaadb6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Tracking data helps you spot trends and fix issues early. If no one looks at reports, you miss chances to improve. Review key metrics often and adjust as needed.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a4f4718 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a4f4718\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Not Seeking Professional Help<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-155118d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"155118d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Sometimes, DIY customization isn\u2019t enough. If your system isn\u2019t working as expected, getting expert support can save time and prevent costly mistakes.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/hubspot\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mountainise HubSpot services<\/a>\u00a0can help optimize your CRM for better performance.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-01fed98 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"01fed98\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-14\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Conclusion<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d5b9d9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6d5b9d9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>HubSpot CRM can do a lot, but it works best when customized to fit your business. The right setup saves time, improves sales, and helps you serve customers better. Keep things simple, train your team, and update data regularly. Use automation wisely and track results to make smart decisions.<\/p><p>Need help customizing HubSpot? We specialize in setup, automation, and optimization to match your business needs.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Contact us today to get the most out of your CRM<\/a>.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-792f8a2\" data-id=\"792f8a2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-d80fe59 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d80fe59\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;],&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&q